  "texts": [
    "Therefore, a selection of key keywords has been made.",
    "These key keywords include blockchain, things, privacy, internet, internet of things, internet of things (IoT), IoT, irrigation, precision agriculture, security, sensors, smart agriculture, wireless sensor network, and wireless sensor networks.",
    "The selection of these keywords was based on their occurrence and link strength in the literature.",
    "Specifically, the co-occurrence links between the keywords Internet and Internet of things had a strength of 250 with 81 occurrences.",
    "Only the keywords with the highest strength are discussed in this study."
